txt.en: 'I shall certainly honour the Red Sky Clan and find suitable places to plant these lights in our travels through Mordor. I hope they have the mysterious properties to heal the land, as you say they do, [placeholder].'

The Red Sky Clan of Bhol Rûdh is up against impossible odds in their conflict with the forces of Seregost.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires Bhol Rûdh: Siege of Corruption to be underway. Bring the Wose lights to Candúr
